data.description: You wont want to miss this very spacious 3 bedroom 1.5 bath ranch home with a full basement! Bring your family and friends over to entertain in the large kitchen and family room! The large basement has many possibilities just waiting for you and your personal touch! This home offers roku security cameras, smart thermostat, water filtration system, small greenhouse, and 2 sheds. You're just minutes away from all the amenities you would need while being in Elgin school district. *** This home offers an additional lot on a separate parcel with 12 beautiful mature fruit trees (peach, apple, cherry) along with blueberry and blackberry bush to be included in purchase! Call today for your showing!
